	<span>PHYSICIANS CHOICE DIALYSIS AFFILIATES WITH THE BULLOCK COUNTY HOSPITAL:</span>
	
<p>	<strong>Union Springs, Alabama.</strong>  Physicians Choice Dialysis is coming into Union Springs area to assist in providing care to those patients who are affected by kidney disease.  Physicians Choice Dialysis will be constructing a newly constructed state of the art building in affiliation with Bullock County Hospital.  This new facility will be state of the art with flat screen televisions, massaging chairs, and highly technological dialysis equipment.  We will proudly offer all modalities including in-center hemodialysis, home hemodialysis and peritoneal dialysis.  These features will allow the patients to receive the best in quality and compassionate care available to kidney patients.  
</p>
<p>	Physicians Choice Dialysis will partner with Montgomery Kidney Specialist; Drs. Michael H. Broder,  Rafael Lopez and Charles Thomas to assure patients are seen on a regularly scheduled basis.  The physician group will be available for referrals from local physicians as well as for office visits and dialysis clinic rounds.  
</p>
<p>	Physicians Choice Dialysis will be opening in the summer of 2011.  Please join us in welcoming the affiliation with Bullock County Hospital, Physicians Choice Dialysis and Montgomery Kidney Specialist into Union Springs.  For more information about this expansion of care in your local area please feel free to contact the company as 334-312-3761 or
	<a href="mailto:information@phychoice.com">information@phychoice.com</a>.
</p>
